{"tid":265143,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)深夜食堂1-2 無聲火 1408","createTime":"2017-05-31T12:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T18:21:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0714a1e11c459ce069463f271b32a8508ac6f3de","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=CVBbksuk%2FbBim1Jn98wMFZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0237eeba\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=CVBbksuk%2FbBim1Jn98wMFZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=751242d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=CVBbksuk%2FbBim1Jn98wMFZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1829594d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b4/Midnight_Diner.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb4%2FMidnight_Diner.jpg&h=8694585c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d7/Bangkok_Dangerous_poster_%282008_American_film_Version%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd7%2FBangkok_Dangerous_poster_%25282008_American_film_Version%2529.jpg&h=ed7ee382&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/63/1408poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F6%2F63%2F1408poster.jpg&h=9f68e8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.午夜12點，在城市的一隅，一家食堂開始營業。菜譜只有豬肉味噌湯，客人想吃的都可以點。這是老闆（小林薰 飾）的經營方針。特殊的風格和懷念的味道，招來了不少的客人。<br />\n大家喝著小酒，吃著自己鍾情的食物，卸下一天的疲憊，談論著遇到的趣事，或是獨自品味憂愁。 在食物的香氣里，在深夜特有的幽靜和食堂內的裊裊暖意間，一齣齣充滿人情味的故事被娓娓道來。有悲有喜，暗合著食物的酸甜苦辣。人生百味，盡在這四方食堂間<br />\n<br />\n2.華燈初上，新宿的某條小巷裡，食堂老闆(小林薰 飾)的一天才正要開始。菜單上只有一道菜和三樣酒，但請隨意點菜，條件若允許就可以料理。營業時間是晚上十二點到早上七點左右，大家都稱這裡作「深夜食堂」。<br />\n聽說男人都抗拒不了穿喪服的寡婦，在出版社擔任編輯的範子(河井青葉 飾)，卻有個奇怪的癖好：穿著喪服、大吃燒肉定食來舒壓。沒想到卻在參加真正的喪禮時，對一面之緣的男子產生好感，她能就此逢凶化吉迎接幸福嗎？<br />\n<br />\n3.喬（尼可拉斯&middot;凱吉飾）原本是個冷血職業殺手，但即將發生意想不到的轉變，一切都要從泰國曼谷說起&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n喬原本前往泰國是要執行任務，他僱用一個街頭混混來幫忙毀滅他殺人的證據。但奇怪的是，一向獨來獨往的他，卻發現和那個街頭混混開始交心。而且還被一個女店員深深吸引了，這讓他覺得他要不要繼續當殺手<br />\n<br />\n4.本片故事描述一位個性鐵齒、只相信自己直覺的恐怖名小說家麥可恩斯林（約翰庫薩克 飾），某晚來到了一家旅舍，負責管理旅社的歐林經理（山繆傑克遜 飾）告訴恩斯林這家旅社有間鬧鬼的禁忌1408房，只要住進1408房的旅客都再也沒活著退房過，不信邪的恩斯林不顧旅社經理的勸告，執意要住進1408房。當恩斯林打開這間禁忌之房的這一刻開始，一切完全超出他原本所預期的詭異許多，這間房門將永遠被鎖上，而房內無法預測的恐怖異象將不時襲擊，恩斯林開始發現這個夜晚將會是個漫漫長夜&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b74e7d7e439c0e9720afe976b0f2bf7658f25f3","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6e4d14721adf2d816cc09a17313b038349540c","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c416c042d0b65a864132b6ac3e22bba859a95734","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66bc1067e6318fe38b7f1ac8d4918a6c41dea73","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1567f79a41b26a23984ad99245a1728d040e472","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea709672e26de6cb768c8debe1541b6416aa3afe","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad90a50dfac20d1dc17b9d05cd7db7232602ca12","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9687ebc07439349f8f3197980017ecc74a1242","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae7799c99638d96bbbe833d3b18579868f287ac","tid":265143,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}